data.text: @AngeliJolie24x7 I hope this message reaches Angelina Jolie

@AngeliJolie24x7 Hi...
Ask you for help, after you have heard about your generosity, and help you did not want to help.
I am stuck with hope that you will help me, I hope you do not disappoint me.
I wish you a quick recovery and ask God to heal you.
I do not speak English.
00962780171249
Jordan
